

1. To view what's written in a file. -cat filename
2. To change the access permissions of files. - chmod 777 
3. To check which commands you have run till now.  - History
4. To remove a directory/ Folder. rm -rf flodername
5. To create a fruits.txt file and to view the content. vim fruits.txt
6. Add content in devops.txt (One in each line) - Apple, Mango, Banana, Cherry, Kiwi, Orange, Guava.
7. To Show only top three fruits from the file. - head -3 fruits.txt
8. To Show only bottom three fruits from the file. tail -3 fruits.txt
9. To create another file Colors.txt and to view the content. - vim colours.txt
10. Add content in Colors.txt (One in each line) - Red, Pink, White, Black, Blue, Orange, Purple, Grey.
11. To find the difference between fruits.txt and Colors.txt file. diff fruits.txt colours.txt
